## Implementation Plan: Migrate from HeyGen Streaming Avatar to LiveAvatar SDK

### Overview of Changes

This migration touches 7 files (3 new, 4 modified) and replaces the deprecated `@heygen/streaming-avatar` SDK with `@heygen/liveavatar-web-sdk@0.0.10`. The key architectural shift is:

- **Old**: `StreamingAvatar` class + manual `MediaStream` attachment via `STREAM_READY` event + `speak({text, taskType: TaskType.REPEAT})` + `createStartAvatar()` / `stopAvatar()`
- **New**: `LiveAvatarSession` class + `session.attach(element)` + `session.repeat(text)` + `session.start()` / `session.stop()` + server-side token from `api.liveavatar.com`

