- `/Users/johnathanmo/mirrorless/frontend/src/hooks/useLiveAvatar.ts` - Core new hook: entire LiveAvatar SDK integration, speech queue, session lifecycle
- `/Users/johnathanmo/mirrorless/frontend/src/app/mirror/page.tsx` - Main re-integration: wires all hooks, components, socket events, and session state together
- `/Users/johnathanmo/mirrorless/backend/routers/heygen.py` - Backend token endpoint: must change API URL, request body, and response format for LiveAvatar
- `/Users/johnathanmo/mirrorless/frontend/src/hooks/useHeyGenAvatar.ts` - Reference for speech queue pattern to port to new hook, then delete
- `/Users/johnathanmo/mirrorless/backend/agent/orchestrator.py` - Add `mira_speech_done` event emission for SentenceBuffer flush timing

